00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:20,480
To get me out of here,

268
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:23,750
you made a life-and-death pact
with Uncle Kun.

269
00:21:27,030 --> 00:21:28,720
You've got so much on your shoulders.

270
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:30,910
I'm sorry.

271
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:34,400
I thought you were setting a trap for me.

272
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,280
Hao Yu,

273
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:42,590
it's my fault.

274
00:21:43,550 --> 00:21:45,030
I should've been honest with you.

275
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:52,720
I did have a past

276
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,830
with Zhou Ziheng,

277
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,590
but that was over a long time ago.

278
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:00,510
I didn't choose him,

279
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,030
and he didn't choose me.

280
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:04,830
For all these years,

281
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,920
because of Officer Guan,

282
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:11,310
my life in Cangfeng has been on the line.

283
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:14,480
I've kept causing you trouble.

284
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:19,200
After Officer Guan died,

285
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,110
Zhou Ziheng showed up.

286
00:22:22,110 --> 00:22:23,070
I didn't expect that.

287
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:26,070
At first, I really

288
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:27,400
planned to tell you,

289
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:29,640
but I was afraid you'd misunderstand me.

290
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,030
So I...

291
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,550
I didn't dare tell you.

292
00:22:38,830 --> 00:22:39,670
It's okay.

293
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:41,790
It's okay, Hao Yu.

294
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,640
Feilong and Uncle Kun

295
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,930
have found out the truth.

296
00:22:45,590 --> 00:22:47,090
This has nothing to do with you.

297
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:49,870
It's okay.

298
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,640
I know you don't believe me,

299
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:56,630
or

300
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,310
don't fully trust me.

301
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,070
But, Ji Zhijie,

302
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,560
I know

303
00:23:06,830 --> 00:23:09,030
you're the only one I have in this world.

304
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,590
Only you can keep me safe.

305
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:20,000
I only have you, Ji Zhijie.

306
00:23:28,510 --> 00:23:29,350
Hao Yu,

307
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:31,960
it's my fault.

308
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:34,960
I should have told you

309
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:35,910
everything.

310
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:38,070
I should have trusted you completely.

311
00:23:40,030 --> 00:23:42,070
Then you wouldn't have been hurt like this.

312
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,320
I'm sorry.

313
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,640
It's not your fault.

314
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:53,760
I know

315
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:56,720
sometimes love

316
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:59,070
only breeds more

317
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:01,510
doubt and misunderstanding.

318
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,550
Let's not do this anymore, okay?

319
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,510
Zhong Jiali must be playing both sides,

320
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:24,350
so she was feeding info to the cops

321
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:25,640
and framing Hao Yu.

322
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:27,760
At the same time,

323
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,750
she colluded with the gangs
to rob the shipment.

324
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,000
Now we've lost the goods,

325
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,320
and she...

326
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,880
Are you sure Zhong Jiali

327
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,880
is the real mole?

328
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:44,800
Uncle Kun.

329
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:54,720
(Zhong Jiali is a dead woman walking anyway.)

330
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,270
(Framing her will save Hao Yu.)

331
00:24:58,310 --> 00:24:59,830
(Then I can keep using Hao Yu)

332
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:02,350
(to finally shake off Liang Zhaokun.)

333
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:05,160
(And I'll find a way)

334
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,200
(to take Hao Yu back from Ji Zhijie.)

335
00:25:12,310 --> 00:25:13,480
Now we've lost the goods.

336
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:17,000
I only care where they are.

337
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:20,200
Who did she collude with?

338
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,030
I'll find out ASAP.

339
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:28,680
Ji Zhijie

340
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:33,030
stays with that woman every day.

341
00:25:33,350 --> 00:25:34,880
He doesn't even care that

342
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:36,070
the goods are missing.

343
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:40,200
Leverage your badge

344
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,790
to track down the goods.

345
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,480
It's your only shot at redemption.

346
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:51,590
Yes, Uncle Kun.

347
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:10,310
I did betray Liang Zhaokun.

348
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:13,110
That's because I despise him.

349
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:14,920
He's a monster.

350
00:26:15,350 --> 00:26:17,070
He's the one who killed my mother,

351
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,510
yet he pretended to save me

352
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:22,960
as my savior.

353
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,110
I admit what I did.

354
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,350
But the tracker?

355
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,350
I didn't plant it.

356
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,160
I won't admit that even if I die!

357
00:26:45,930 --> 00:26:46,870
It doesn't matter now.

358
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,920
The word on the street is

359
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:51,200
Cangfeng and I killed Suchart

360
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,400
and took the haul.

361
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:55,030
No one else in Seronport would dare do that.

362
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,550
Just tell me.

363
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:08,440
Who exactly is your contact?

364
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:10,750
Where are the goods?

365
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:22,110
That's the biggest joke I've ever heard.

366
00:27:23,750 --> 00:27:25,510
Will you let us go if we tell you?

367
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:28,760
Ji Zhijie,

368
00:27:29,720 --> 00:27:31,160
we're all from the same gutter.

369
00:27:31,830 --> 00:27:32,920
Do you think I'd believe you?

370
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,080
Pfft!

371
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,280
Ji Zhijie,

372
00:27:37,550 --> 00:27:38,750
whether you're Uncle Kun's wolf

373
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,920
or his dog,

374
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:41,400
just do your job.

375
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:43,590
We're dead anyway.

376
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:45,640
But before we die,

377
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:47,880
we just want to be human for once!

378
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,270
Save your breath.

379
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,070
I'm not telling you anything.

380
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,270
Ji Zhijie.

381
00:28:06,310 --> 00:28:08,270
You're more pathetic than we are.

382
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:11,270
Liang Zhaokun played you like a fool.

383
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:13,110
And you're going to die

384
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:15,880
at the hands of the woman you love most-

385
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:22,680
Hao Yu.

386
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:27,830
Hao Yu!

387
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:34,880
For the sake of our childhood friendship,

388
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,490
I told Uncle Kun

389
00:28:39,220 --> 00:28:40,110
I wanted to keep you safe.

390
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:44,020
Since you don't want that...

391
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,800
I swore

392
00:28:57,750 --> 00:28:58,790
I wouldn't kill again.

393
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,110
Do it yourselves.

394
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,320
Weihao.

395
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:19,590
It's okay.

396
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:21,590
I'm right here with you.

397
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:27,000
I'm with you too.

398
00:29:31,270 --> 00:29:32,110
I'm so sorry for

399
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:34,880
everything you went through.

400
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:45,000
In our next life,

401
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,480
let's not be born in Seronport.

402
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:09,510
And let's not just be friends.

